description.en: Hydrocarbon 8 (UK) LTD, the international oil & gas project management company, is pleased to announce the unique of its kind placement of security tokens (STO) with total value of 89 mln CHF backed by oil and gas developing projects in MENA (Middle East, North Africa) countries. The offer will be launched on the 8th of August 2018 and will last for 60 days.The placement will be commenced in parallel with traditional private placement to utilize hybrid financing opportunities. The company allow investors to convert tokens into company ordinary shares with subsequent listing on the reputable traditional stock exchange to secure additional liquidity.
